# Next.js App Router Patterns

- Pages are `'use client'` with default exports
- Dynamic routes use `use(params)` to unwrap the params Promise (Next.js 15 pattern, see `src/app/artwork/[id]/page.tsx`)
- API routes export named HTTP method handlers: `export async function POST(request: NextRequest)`
- Root layout in `src/app/layout.tsx` imports `Header` and `globals.css`
- Use `next/image` with `firebasestorage.googleapis.com` in allowed domains (`next.config.ts`)
- Loading states: use `LoadingSpinner` component while data fetches
